# GEOsphere

GEOsphere is a standalone GEO audit engine built from scratch for deterministic collection, scoring, and reporting.

## Quick start

```bash
cd GEOsphere
python -m pip install -e .[dev]
python -m geosphere audit https://example.com
python -m geosphere quick https://example.com
pytest
```

## Commands

```bash
python -m geosphere audit <url> --max-pages 12 --output runs
python -m geosphere quick <url>
python -m geosphere inspect <url>
python -m geosphere llms <url>
python -m geosphere compare <run-a> <run-b>
python -m geosphere benchmark <primary-url> <competitor-url> [more]
python -m geosphere install-skill
```

## Output

Each audit creates a run directory containing `audit.json`, `audit.md`, `summary.json`, `robots.json`, `sitemap.json`, `pages.json`, `llms.txt`, `llms-full.txt`, and collected artifacts.
